Package: FootballOffStatCalc
Type: Package
Title: Football Offensive Statistics Calculation Package
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Brandon Dora
Date: 2021-4-21
Maintainer: Brandon Dora <bmd2@usf.edu>
Description: This package is intended to provide the user with easy and convenient functions, so that way the user can calculate most major offensive stat lines, 
given user-input data, that are relevant to professional football. In order to use this package, simply type any of the fuctions and input your basic user statistical data,
and the program will calculate all of the major statlines on the Offensive-side of American Football. For a list of functions within this package, type hello() to start.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
